# Surface reactions for ambipolar ions striking the satellite.
# Each ambipolar ion recombines with its electron to form the parent neutral
# (ion + e -> neutral). Format matches SPARTA "surf_react prob" style; see
# sparta/examples/ambi/air.surf and the surf_react doc page.

O+ --> O
E S 1.0

O2+ --> O2
E S 1.0

NO+ --> NO
E S 1.0

N+ --> N
E S 1.0

N2+ --> N2
E S 1.0
